high_descs: Turn left and go to the white trash can
Take the sponge out of the trash can
Turn left and go to the counter with the pan on it
Put the sponge in the pan
Pick up the sponge and pan from the counter
Turn left and go to the sink on the right
Place the sponge and pan in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge and pan in a sink

high_descs: Walk to the garbage that's in front of you to the left and stand facing it.
Pick up the sponge that's in front of you in the garbage.
Turn left and take a step to your left then walk to the counter in front of you.
Put the sponge in the frying pan to your right on the counter.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it.
Take a step or two to your left to face the ink.
Put the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a sponge in it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the white bin to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the sponge from the bin.
Walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the sponge in the pan on the right.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Walk to the sink on the left.
Put the pan down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the sponge in the pan and put the pan in the sink.
